              <h3 class="question">How long can I stay?</h3>
              <p>Your stay will be expected to be overnight only. You will need to check out of the room by 2pm on the following day.</p>
              <p>If clinical circumstances mean that your stay in hospital for more than one night you will have to move to the normal ward as you and your baby need to be medically fit to remain in these rooms.</p>
