              <h3 class="question">What can my partner expect?</h3>
              <p>Your partner will be offered breakfast in the room, and can access the tea and coffee making facilities. There is a coffee shop within the Jessop Wing for all other meals and snacks which your partner might want to purchase.</p>
            </div>
